{"tid":311742,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你是我 這一輩子都不想失聯的愛","createTime":"2017-07-07T01:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T06:42:57.000Z","uid":45705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7982077cd06c341fdf4442dc9875091d4f2636f3","tid":311742,"uid":45705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T01:09:42.000Z","msg":"我猜你一定也會想念我<br />\n也怕我失落在茫茫人海 <br />\n沒關係只要你肯回頭望<br />\n會發現我一直都在<br />\n<br />\n你給我 這一輩子都不想失聯的愛<br />\n你的每條訊息都是心跳節拍<br />\n每秒都想 擁你入懷<br />\n全世界你最可愛<br />\n<br />\n你是我 這一輩子都不想失聯的愛<br />\n就算你的呼吸遠在千山之外<br />\n請你相信 我給的愛<br />\n值得你愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8bb6b4813f88c22c93d3665abf41b3d0ed2d65","tid":311742,"uid":105067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T01:13:07.000Z","msg":"超好聽"},{"pid":"df7c8e38096e9aaa6431f7f98880599d8758b74b","tid":311742,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超好聽</blockquote><br />\nangel方加"},{"pid":"5de59f9b3a2ed18dcd7bb6653a3cf5d10fc2b667","tid":311742,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"前排係咁loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ca80c8fcf510ee4f9f0f9a752495af17996069","tid":311742,"uid":45705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排係咁loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n愈聽愈入心入肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}